cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV, cs.EM 

The paper involves the use of machine learning techniques for occupancy recognition, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of model predictive control for HVAC operations falls under the category of cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves the use of simulation for building thermal response, which falls under the category of cs.SY (Systems and Control). The use of video processing for occupancy recognition falls under the category of cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper involves the implementation of an embedded system, which falls under the category of cs.EM (Embedded Systems).
